  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). NOTE: ValidationResult vr-hemolysis-01 was generated under ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which the team characterises as effectively identical to the released build 2026-q1-build-7; validation was not re-executed under the released solver.",
