      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index (RHI) compared against FDA centrifugal blood pump experimental dataset across 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean RHI error 4.2%; all operating points satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The team noted that build 2026-q1-build-7-rc2 differs from the released build 2026-q1-build-7 only in a patch to the turbulence wall-function residual convergence criterion and judged re-execution unnecessary.",
