        "description": "Ansys CFX 15.0 solver configuration used for all hemolysis validation runs. Steady-state SST k-omega turbulence model; power-law hemolysis damage accumulation model (Giersiepen coefficients). Mesh: 4.1 M hexahedral elements; y+ < 5 at blade surfaces. Convergence: RMS residuals < 1e-5. This build is the release candidate immediately preceding the production release; the only change in the GA release (2026-q1-build-7) was a minor fix to turbulence wall-function residual normalisation that the development team characterised as numerically inconsequential for this class of flow. Validation was conducted on rc2 three weeks before the GA release date and was not repeated on the GA build."
