    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Validation results demonstrate CFD RHI prediction error within 10% acceptance criterion across all operating points. The assessment team noted that validation runs were executed under pre-release build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 rather than the released production build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7, but concluded that the single patch-level change (turbulence wall-function residual normalisation) is numerically inconsequential for this flow regime and that re-execution is not warranted. On this basis the credibility package is accepted and the model is considered fit for the stated COU at Medium assurance level.",
